author: xavier
msg: use getDependencyRevisionId instead of getDynamicConstraintRevisionId to check version matching, since dependency mediation is done before sorting, and keeping it like this makes build relying on version matcher and build specific resources (like a properties file) fail when the resource is not loaded, while the revConstraint should not be used.
